#31318
the Pine Forest~
   Deep in the forest you have exits in all four cardinal directions.  East
will take you further from the road.  West will do the opposite.  North,
forest, and southmore forest.  Looking up your view of the sky is limited by
the tree limbs and vegetation.  The ground is moist, thick with pine straw and
moss.  
